snippet.title: Puppets by Arlee
snippet.description:
I am a puppeteer and puppet builder.  Here is where you can find free video tutorials and performances.  Please enjoy!

 🗓 Channel Schedule:
New video every Monday at 10am NYC time

I hope you enjoy my content ❤️ 
If you do please consider subscribing 👍and don't forget to hit the bell 🔔 !! 
Thanks for your support !! ❤🥰

📧 Email: puppetsbyarlee@gmail.com

Want to support this channel? 
paypal.me/puppetsbyarlee
